{
  "stem": "5891.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had the little [GERMAN], they call it, hanging on there for lights, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no street lights on those side streets like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But sometimes we drove late at night or very early in the morning, about 4 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I mean, you didn't have to worry about traffic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no cars going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was with the horse and the wagons, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the weather condition had a lot to do with the traveling plans, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he kind of knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were three days, sometimes a week, sometimes two weeks, on some of those parking spots where we would park.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes only three days or two days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All depends how the-- the business was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They make a living, of course, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it sounds unbelievable, but it's a gorgeous life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Beautiful, happy, happy, happy life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If I had to do it all over again, I would do it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Even now, my 70 years old, I would do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beautiful town, as-- as you've see in some of the pictures I showed you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a small town.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's not that small anymore now, but it was-- I think there were 900 or 1,200 [INAUDIBLE] at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's going to be a big city now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But everybody knew everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The schools, you know, wonderful teachers, and everybody admired our lives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They always said, oh, I wish I could-- and many times, we did take some from the neighbors with us for the summer.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Schmidt or Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Johnson, whoever it was, came to see my mother and said, oh, yeah, Ellie wants to go with you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So some-- you got enough of your own, but always one of them came along.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
